high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then turn left to face the microwave.
Pick up the large spoon, to the right of the microwave.
Turn around and move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Clean the large spoon in the sink.
Turn right and move forward, then turn right and step forward, then turn around to face the cabinets beneath the counter.
Open the rightmost cabinet in front of you and put the large spoon inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large spoon in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the microwave on the counter on the left.
Pick up the spoon on the counter.
Bring the spoon the the sink, right of the microwave.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Bring the spoon to the right, to the corner of the counter.
Put the cleaned spoon in the lower right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the microwave on the left.
Pick up the ladle on the right of the microwave.
Turn around and move to the sink on the left.
Put the ladle in the sink, wash the ladle, and pick up the ladle again.
Turn to the right and face the cupboards right of the sink.
Put the ladle into the cupboard on the far right.
anns.task_desc: Clean the ladle and put it away into the cupboard.
